{"tid":766359,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【辱華無極限】遍佈全球角落！ 外國人開拖專鬧「強國人」","createTime":"2018-08-03T13:59:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T08:49:51.000Z","uid":179810,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7c5cbba600c10a9466904a0e338113dd94c8ddd5","tid":766359,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:59:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180802/58512631\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F58512631&d=6OPC8sVgRcWF6f2wRpSeoTACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=bfcb0302\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F58512631&h=de338d34\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180802/58512631</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180801/large/1533128564_0309.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180801%2Flarge%2F1533128564_0309.jpg&h=00405f70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n新西蘭華人因為勸阻他人餵飼野鴨，被外國人舉中指及辱罵。(互聯網)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n加拿大多倫多地鐵，發生加國惡女大罵華裔中年女「滾回中國」，在當地被廣泛報道。不過，類似事件不斷發生在世界各地，一名在新西蘭奧克蘭的華人，只是因為勸助別人不要餵飼湖中的野鴨，被人大罵「滾回中國」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n這名被罵的華人女子姓孫，她表示今年6月她在奧克蘭的Western Springs公園，向兩名外籍遊客說不要餵飼野鴨，因為他們餵飼的食物會在湖中腐化，影響水質，令野鴨死亡。可是，兩名遊客對她舉中指、並且出言辱罵，更要她「滾回中國」。孫女稱，新西蘭人大多數都很友善，但有些人卻不喜歡中國人，會對她說很粗魯的話。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n同樣情況亦曾發生在新加坡，一名當地男子今年6月在一個美食廣場，向一名來自中國的女侍應說外賣要分開打包，可是女侍應不懂英文，一直都在說普通話，男子便當眾的大罵：「不會講英文就滾回自己的國家，你不能要求我講中文，你來到新加坡，這是我的國家，我是新加坡人！」片段在fb廣傳，同樣成為熱話。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n在今年4月底，來自浙江嘉興的女子張丹童，在西班牙福恩吉羅拉乘坐火車時，遭到一眾當地學生侮辱，向她扔煙蒂，拍打她的頭部，更罵她「Puta China」（中國婊子）和「他X的滾回你的中國」（China de mierda vuelve a tu pa&iacute;s），她忍無可忍，用手機拍下，將片段上傳到fb，西班牙國家警察調查後，已拘捕兩名未滿20歲的少年被捕。<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFacebook"},{"pid":"90d3a03557e88fd9e39a1d249dbe81a969dfdcde","tid":766359,"uid":41368,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:01:14.000Z","msg":"做得好！"},{"pid":"deb173ff3da697c6df3701648e33974a0cc1ab79","tid":766359,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:03:14.000Z","msg":"已拘捕兩名未滿20歲的少年被捕。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6dec07de1a34be6cf6d94ecc70f490f1c4f155","tid":766359,"uid":153689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"deb173ff3da697c6df3701648e33974a0cc1ab79","tid":766359,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:03:14.000Z","msg":"已拘捕兩名未滿20歲的少年被捕。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:06:29.000Z","msg":"香港記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70be9ff2d693019ad94c36a9561d50d7c863477b","tid":766359,"uid":116364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:06:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcee84f5cb530f6cc3b4ce479a49c705aa7e36a9","tid":766359,"uid":116364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:07:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54e19d0446cd15dc82f4eb7f61093b5d86817776","tid":766359,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:13:19.000Z","msg":"HK is not China<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d11a9aad74b192e1171c510b94480e180da2d1db","tid":766359,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:24:47.000Z","msg":"真無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf4494af9feb4806a0f2a22642c2983d115eff0","tid":766359,"uid":10014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:29:38.